<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
<div class="lp-part-1">
  <div class="lp-block-1">
    <h1>找到战友 一起进步</h1>
        <h2>有理想的人不应该缺少同行者，成长的路上不再孤军奋战</h2>
    <div>
        <%= link_to("立刻体验", courses_path, class:"lp-block-1-button") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="lp-part-2">
  <div class="lp-block-2">
    <h2>我相信，你并不孤独</h2>
    <div class="block-p">
      <p class="advantages">
        为了那个更好的自己和更好的未来，你在默默努力，这个过程注定伴随着痛苦
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-pom-box-47">
      <span class="pom-box"><i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
      <h3>终身学习者在这里找到同类</h3>
      <p>发布你正在学习的课程与技能，分享你的学习经验</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-pom-box-47">
      <span class="pom-box"><i class="fa fa-pagelines" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
      <h3>构建属于自己成长环境</h3>
      <p>跳出屏幕，在你的城市组织一次学习者的聚会</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-pom-box-47">
      <span class="pom-box"><i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
      <h3>成长记录</h3>
      <p>看到自己生长的过程，未来的你一定会感谢自己今天的努力</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="lp-logo fa fa-play-circle-o fa-3x" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" >
  <img class="logo2", src='/images/logo2.png'></img>
<!-- Button trigger modal -->
</div>
<!-- Modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-body">
          <iframe height=498 width=510 src='https://player.youku.com/embed/XMjcyNDQyMTk0NA==' frameborder=0 'allowfullscreen'></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!--part 4 -->
<div class="lp-part-4">
<div class="lp-block-content">
  <p class="block-title">
    课程推荐
  </p>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
    	    <div class="well">
                <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide">

                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                </ol>

                <!-- Carousel items -->
                <div class="carousel-inner">

                <div class="item active">
                  <div class="row-fluid">
                  <% Course.published.recent.limit(3).each do |course| %>
                	  <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                      <div class="thumbnail2 custab">
                      <a href="<%= course_path(course) %>"><img src="<%= course.image.url(:medium)%>" alt="Image"/></a></div>
                      </div>
                  <% end %>
                	</div><!--/row-fluid-->
                </div><!--/item-->

                <div class="item">
                  <div class="row-fluid">
                  <% Course.published.recent.offset(3).limit(3).each do |course| %>
                	  <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4"><a href="<%= course_path(course) %>">
                      <div class="thumbnail2 custab">
                      <img src="<%= course.image.url(:medium)%>" alt="Image" /></a></div>
                      </div>
                  <% end %>
                	</div><!--/row-fluid-->
                </div><!--/item-->

                </div><!--/carousel-inner-->

                <a class="left carousel-control" class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span></a>
                <a class="right carousel-control" class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span></a>
                </div><!--/myCarousel-->

            </div><!--/well-->
      </div>
  </div>


</div>

</div>



